@host = http://localhost:3000
@date = 2025-11-15

### 1) Health
GET {{host}}/health

### 2) Create Venue (copy _id from response)
POST {{host}}/api/venues
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Meeting Room A",
  "description": "Ruang meeting modern dengan proyektor",
  "capacity": 10,
  "price_per_hour": 100000,
  "amenities": ["Proyektor", "Whiteboard", "AC"]
}

### 2a) SET THIS to the _id you just got
@venueId = 692ec773a6ae8240e199ab5d

### 3) Get Venue
GET {{host}}/api/venues/{{venueId}}

### 4) Check Availability
GET {{host}}/api/venues/{{venueId}}/availability/{{date}}

### 5) Create Booking (use a listed slot; change user_id to a 24-hex string you control)
# If you don't have users yet, generate one with:
# node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(12).toString('hex'))"
@userId = 673f1234567890abcdef5678

POST {{host}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}",
  "venue_id": "{{venueId}}",
  "date": "{{date}}",
  "start_time": "09:30",
  "duration": 1
}

### 5a) SET THIS to the bookingId returned above
@bookingId = 692ec793a6ae8240e199ab5e

### 6) Get User Bookings
GET {{host}}/api/users/{{userId}}/bookings

### 7) Cancel Booking
DELETE {{host}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}

### 8) Check Availability again
GET {{host}}/api/venues/{{venueId}}/availability/{{date}}
